## MinigameBridge.cs
Singleton, DontDestroyOnLoad. Handles all scene transitions between city and minigames.

**Flow:**
```
CrisisMarker clicked
→ BeginMinigame(sceneName, marker)
    → pauses timer (gameActive = false)
    → loads minigame scene

Player finishes minigame
→ ReturnToCity(bool success)
    → resumes timer (gameActive = true)
    → loads city scene
    → notifies CrisisMarker via OnMinigameReturned(success)
```

**Key notes:**
- Stores `_pendingMarker` and `_citySceneName` across scene boundary
- `NotifyMarkerAfterLoad` waits one frame after city scene loads before notifying marker — this is intentional, gives scene time to initialize
- Currently stubbed with Debug.Log in minigame scenes since not yet placed in scene

