## CityHUD.cs
Drives the city UI. Subscribes to `GameManager.OnHPChanged`.

**UI elements needed:**
- `timerLabel` (TMP) — shows `M:SS` format
- `timerBar` (Image, filled horizontal) — depletes with time
- `hpLabel` (TMP) — shows `HP: 4/5`
- `hpHearts[]` (Image array) — heart icons, disabled as HP drops
- `scoreLabel` (TMP) — live score, updates every frame

