## Setup Order (when ready to hook up)
1. Create empty GameObject `GameManager` in city scene
2. Attach `GameManager.cs` + `MinigameBridge.cs` + `CrisisSpawner.cs`
3. Create Canvas in city scene, attach `CityHUD.cs`, wire up UI elements
4. Place empty GameObjects across city as crisis spawn points, assign to CrisisSpawner
5. Fill in CrisisTypes list with each minigame's scene name + settings
6. Add `CrisisMarker` prefab to CrisisSpawner
7. Hook up Main Menu Play button to `GameManager.Instance.StartGame()`
8. Create GameOver scene that reads PlayerPrefs for final score display

